# Module 1 - Basics
## Level 5 - Challenge 2

Problem
Take your name and age from the user and print a message.

Instructions
1. Ask the user to enter name.
2. Ask the user to enter age.
3. Print a message with both values.

Example Input
Rahul
20

Example Output
Hello Rahul
You are 20 years old

Hint
Use input() for both values and print them using print().

Broken Code
name = input("Enter name: ")
age = input("Enter age: ")
print("Hello" name)
print("You are", age "years old")

Correct Code
name = input("Enter name: ")
age = input("Enter age: ")
print("Hello", name)
print("You are", age, "years old")
